    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一张纸生活在常年下雨的小镇中，它每天下班回家都要用雨伞抵挡各处来的溅水，它真的很讨厌下雨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192360/extras/cce0acd98f0f6033e961b40dfe14e86c.avif?t=1758426810\" width=150 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-在手绘风格的世界中感受下雨天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级可爱的人物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-与氛围契合的沉浸音乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-体会主角对待雨天态度的变化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去感受下雨吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时长在30分钟左右</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏反馈QQ群：992719842</p>",
